moji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fe85bcda45ccc5b74fffcb5fff62cf5d7e2a4c8","tid":21193,"uid":336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T14:21:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有人想問通識陪世史都可以問 我兩科都5*<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n通識點操<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n個陣時係做oscar ma啲卷 做左應該有40份到<br />\n多做拆題 要對啲概念詞熟先識拆 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n用熟基本嘅框架 政經社文環 個人家庭社會國家國際<br />\n基本上計好時間做到呢啲都有4或者以上<br />\n再背吓啲百搭例子就輕鬆好grade<br />\n駁論邏輯不外乎係 正反效果 可補償嘅 治標治本 應然同實然條件 因果關係 針對持分者個啲</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有無咩百搭例子分享下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 老老豆豆真係唔係好記得<br />\n我係讀用新聞就會記低大約件事 之後拆題就用到<br />\n通常都係用例子引伸例子<br />\n例如：反國教雨革魚革<br />\n&gt; 引伸網絡動員 + 社政參與 + 青少年被煽動（個人成長）+ 公民抗命 + 公民社會 <br />\n或者中共打壓維權<br />\n&gt; 引伸法治四層次 + 軟實力 + 管治效能 + 認受性 + 維穩 <br />\n隨口都可以引伸到其實就唔會寫唔到嘢"},{"pid":"3b41c132564bdd52fd98563d0d51cf4e3dc24e83","tid":21193,"uid":45055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T14:28:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>好驚英文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n英文真係唔洗太怕 我英文溫嘅唔算多 但paper 3係做漏半個task都4 speaking平時練吓夠自然流暢都5* 好易拉到4</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好離地喎"},{"pid":"9f02afc41f103f8a8a17b40c5bfd9e7ee5096c40","tid":21193,"uid":38675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T16:28:28.000Z","msg":"英文如果淆底一定係練listening task<br />\n呢份卷好撚抵操<br />\n信我 搵pts其實真係唔太難<br />\n<br />\n呢份卷應該係你成科英文食糊卷嚟<br />\n一定要操